üïí Date & Time Formatting Cheat Sheet (strftime codes)

üìÜ Date Codes
Code	Meaning	Example
%Y	Year (4 digits)	2025
%y	Year (2 digits)	25
%m	Month (01-12)	04
%B	Month name (full)	April
%b	Month name (short)	Apr
%d	Day of the month (01-31)	03
%A	Weekday (full)	Thursday
%a	Weekday (short)	Thu
%w	Weekday (0=Sunday)	4
%j	Day of the year (001-366)	094

‚è∞ Time Codes
Code	Meaning	Example
%H	Hour (24-hour)	14
%I	Hour (12-hour)	02
%p	AM or PM	PM
%M	Minute (00-59)	45
%S	Second (00-59)	10
%f	Microseconds (000000-999999)	123456

üß© Other Useful Codes
Code	Meaning	Example
%Z	Time zone	UTC
%z	UTC offset	+0300
%c	Local date & time	Thu Apr 3 14:45:10 2025
%x	Local date	04/03/25 (depends on locale)
%X	Local time	14:45:10
